Oh, hey.

12:04.516 --> 12:05.642
Charlotte, come on in.

12:05.892 --> 12:07.102
- Hey, man.
- Hey.

12:09.271 --> 12:11.273
God, it... place smells
like fish sells in here.

12:11.732 --> 12:14.234
